OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FQueen's pony Emma named    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhorse of a lifetime        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The late Queen's favourite riding pony 
OL,6, Emma, has been named horse of a        
OL,7, lifetime at the Horse & Hound awards.  
OL,9,FThe fell pony, who made a poignant     
OL,10,Fappearance at the late monarch's       
OL,11,Ffuneral, won the accolade following a  
OL,12,Fpublic vote.                           
OL,14,FThe award and a bag of carrots was     
OL,15,Faccepted by Lizzie Briant, who competed
OL,16,Fon Emma in showing classes.            
OL,18,FShe said: "Everybody adores her at the 
OL,19,FRoyal Mews - there isn't a pony in the 
OL,20,Fcountry that is better loved."         
